nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, by author Michael A. Stackpole. The audiobook was performed by Chuck Benson and was released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2012.
